33
00:01:58.292 --> 00:02:01.591
WE'LL MAKE THIS GO AWAY.
ALANA.

34
00:02:01.591 --> 00:02:03.159
ARE YOU STARING
AT MY BREASTS. LUTHER?

35
00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:06.925
NO. NO. JUST MARVELING
