71
00:03:32.558 --> 00:03:34.958
SIR.
ARE YOU MICHAEL STRATHMORE?

72
00:03:34.958 --> 00:03:36.925
YES. WHAT'S GOING ON?
SIR. YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

73
00:03:36.925 --> 00:03:38.125
