95
00:04:33.125 --> 00:04:35.558
IT'S ALL A BIG GAMBLE ANYWAY.
ISN'T IT?

96
00:04:35.558 --> 00:04:37.025
I MEAN. WHAT ARE THE ODDS

97
00:04:37.025 --> 00:04:39.259
I'M GONNA FALL IN LOVE
