AND WANT TO TO GET MARRIED
FOR THE EIGHTH TIME? (chuckles)

99
00:04:42.691 --> 00:04:46.259
FATE IS ONE CRAZY MOTHERFUCKER.
IT'S LIKE I TELL MICHAEL--

100
