137
00:06:18.259 --> 00:06:19.691
(calling)

138
00:06:19.691 --> 00:06:21.225
(chattering)

139
00:06:21.225 --> 00:06:24.525
(both grunting)

140
00:06:24.525 --> 00:06:26.558
(chattering)

141
